00:20:52.090 --> 00:20:53.050
Okay.

00:20:53.050 --> 00:20:54.420
Let's benchmark

00:20:55.260 --> 00:20:59.960
Now, so this is on a Mac Pro AMD GPU.

00:20:59.990 --> 00:21:02.700
And this is what we
